        crossfadeSeconds: 0.2
    - rid: 4444056937922035889
      type: {class: VNLineStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: step_104
        label: 
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        speakerId: ????
        pose: 0
        emotion: 0
        sfxId: 
        text: Oh, I love that old trick with the petals! Kaitora's really just a
          hopeless romantic at heart.
        addToLog: 1
        nextStepId: step_105
    - rid: 4444056937922035892
      type: {class: VNLineStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: step_113
        label: 
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        speakerId: Hinato
        pose: 0
        emotion: 0
        sfxId: 
        text: 'One thing about us, is we turn every strong feeling into magic. I
          mean, how cool is that? '
        addToLog: 1
        nextStepId: step_114
    - rid: 4444056937922035893
      type: {class: VNLineStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: step_115
        label: 
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        speakerId: Hinato
        pose: 0
        emotion: 0
        sfxId: 
        text: Are you someone who is more organized or playful?
        addToLog: 1
        nextStepId: 
    - rid: 4444056937922035896
      type: {class: VNChoiceStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: step_116
        label: 
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        options:
        - text: I'm more organized, than playful.
          nextStepId: step_117
          kind: 0
          premiumPrice: 0
          effects: []
        - text: 'I''m more playful, than organized. '
          nextStepId: step_118
          kind: 0
          premiumPrice: 0
          effects: []
    - rid: 4444056937922035897
      type: {class: VNLineStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: step_119
        label: 
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        speakerId: Hinato
        pose: 0
        emotion: 0
        sfxId: 
        text: Hold on! I'm writing that down. Just kidding. My memory's impeccable.
        addToLog: 1
        nextStepId: step_120
    - rid: 4444056937922035902
      type: {class: VNLineStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: step_120
        label: 
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        speakerId: Hinato
        pose: 0
        emotion: 6
        sfxId: 
        text: And this brings us to our next question. I swear, it's part of the
          assignment...
        addToLog: 1
        nextStepId: 
    - rid: 4444056937922035903
      type: {class: VNLineStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: step_121
        label: 
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        speakerId: Hinato
        pose: 0
        emotion: 0
        sfxId: 
        text: What does your ideal weekend look like?
        addToLog: 1
        nextStepId: step_122
    - rid: 4444056937922035904
      type: {class: VNChoiceStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: step_122
        label: 
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        options:
        - text: Hanging out with friends. It really boosts my energy!
          nextStepId: step_124
          kind: 0
          premiumPrice: 0
          effects: []
        - text: 'Staying in, doing my favorite things, so I can recharge. '
          nextStepId: step_123
          kind: 0
          premiumPrice: 0
          effects: []
    - rid: 4444056937922035905
      type: {class: VNLineStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: step_125
        label: 
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        speakerId: Hinato
        pose: 0
        emotion: 5
        sfxId: 
        text: Nice one. And I got all my answers! I guess, we can call it a day...
        addToLog: 1
        nextStepId: step_126
    - rid: 4444056937922035906
      type: {class: VNLineStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: step_126
        label: 
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        speakerId: Lumis
        pose: 0
        emotion: 6
        sfxId: 
        text: Master Hinato! Are you sure you don't have any more questions for our
          candidate?
        addToLog: 1
        nextStepId: step_127
    - rid: 4444056937922035907
      type: {class: VNLineStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: step_127
        label: 
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        speakerId: 
        pose: 0
        emotion: 0
        sfxId: 
        text: Hinato winks mischievously at Lumis.
        addToLog: 1
        nextStepId: step_128
    - rid: 4444056937922035908
      type: {class: VNLineStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: step_128
        label: 
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        speakerId: Hinato
        pose: 0
        emotion: 1
        sfxId: 
        text: Ah, you're adorable, little Lumis! What's the point of asking questions
          if we can just feel it?
        addToLog: 1
        nextStepId: step_129
    - rid: 4444056937922035909
      type: {class: VNLineStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: step_130
        label: 
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        speakerId: 
        pose: 0
        emotion: 0
        sfxId: 
        text: "Lumis blinks, clearly not quite catching what his superior is saying.
          Hinato laughs, and you join in because his laughter\u2019s just so contagious."
        addToLog: 1
        nextStepId: step_131
    - rid: 4444056937922035910
      type: {class: VNLineStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: step_132
        label: 
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        speakerId: Hinato
        pose: 0
        emotion: 6
        sfxId: 
        text: So, how are you doing?
        addToLog: 1
        nextStepId: 
    - rid: 4444056937922035911
      type: {class: VNChoiceStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: step_133
        label: 
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        options:
        - text: I'm having a blast! It was nice to meet all the mentors.
          nextStepId: step_134
          kind: 0
          premiumPrice: 0
          effects: []
        - text: I'm dying to know the results!
          nextStepId: step_134
          kind: 0
          premiumPrice: 0
          effects: []
    - rid: 4444056937922035912
      type: {class: VNLineStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: step_134
        label: 
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        speakerId: Hinato
        pose: 0
        emotion: 0
        sfxId: 
        text: Awesome. Now look! There's something in your sleeve!
        addToLog: 1
        nextStepId: step_135
    - rid: 4444056937922035913
      type: {class: VNLineStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: step_135
        label: 
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        speakerId: 
        pose: 0
        emotion: 0
        sfxId: 
        text: 'You pull a card with a heart drawn on it out of your sleeve. '
        addToLog: 1
        nextStepId: step_139
    - rid: 4444056937922035914
      type: {class: VNLineStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: step_142
        label: 
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        speakerId: 
        pose: 0
        emotion: 0
        sfxId: 
        text: '"Keep that flame burning, little spark!"'
        addToLog: 1
        nextStepId: step_143
    - rid: 4444056937922035915
      type: {class: VNLineStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: step_143
        label: 
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        speakerId: Lumis
        pose: 0
        emotion: 6
        sfxId: 
        text: Uh... that was fun, right?
        addToLog: 1
        nextStepId: step_144
    - rid: 4444056937922035916
      type: {class: VNLineStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: step_144
        label: 
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        speakerId: Lumis
        pose: 0
        emotion: 0
        sfxId: 
        text: 'And now it''s time for you to find out the results of your magic personality
          sorting test. '
        addToLog: 1
