    - rid: 4444057140391575626
      type: {class: VNLineStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: step_013
        label: 
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        speakerId: Lumis
        pose: 0
        emotion: 0
        sfxId: 
        text: 'Each mentor will ask you three questions. By the end of the test,
          you''ll know which faculty you''re in! '
        addToLog: 1
        nextStepId: 
    - rid: 4444057140391575632
      type: {class: VNLineStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: step_024
        label: 
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        speakerId: Shinrai
        pose: 0
        emotion: 5
        sfxId: 
        text: So let us see how you reason.
        addToLog: 1
        nextStepId: step_025
    - rid: 4444057140391575633
      type: {class: VNLineStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: step_048
        label: 
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        speakerId: Kensui
        pose: 0
        emotion: 0
        sfxId: 
        text: 'Take a deep breath and let your spirit speak for you. '
        addToLog: 1
        nextStepId: step_049
    - rid: 4444057140391575635
      type: {class: VNChoiceStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: step_066
        label: 
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        options:
        - text: 'The fact that I have a strong sense of reality. '
          nextStepId: step_067
          kind: 0
          premiumPrice: 0
          effects: []
        - text: My vivid imagination.
          nextStepId: step_068
          kind: 0
          premiumPrice: 0
          effects: []
    - rid: 4444057140391575637
      type: {class: VNLineStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: step_065
        label: 
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        speakerId: Kensui
        pose: 0
        emotion: 0
        sfxId: 
        text: What do you appreciate more in yourself?
        addToLog: 1
        nextStepId: step_066
    - rid: 4444057140391575641
      type: {class: VNLineStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: step_072
        label: 
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        speakerId: 
        pose: 0
        emotion: 0
        sfxId: 
        text: 'He nods at you and Kensui, and Kensui smiles at him calmly before
          he vanishes into the fog.

'
        addToLog: 1
        nextStepId: step_073
    - rid: 4444057140391575642
      type: {class: VNLineStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: step_078
        label: 
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        speakerId: Kaitora
        pose: 0
        emotion: 5
        sfxId: 
        text: That is, if you have what it takes.
        addToLog: 1
        nextStepId: step_079
    - rid: 4444057140391575643
      type: {class: VNLineStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: step_109
        label: 
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        speakerId: 
        pose: 0
        emotion: 0
        sfxId: 
        text: Hinato bows to you, a mischievous grin flickering on his lips.
        addToLog: 1
        nextStepId: step_110
    - rid: 4444057140391575644
      type: {class: VNLineStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: step_114
        label: 
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        speakerId: Hinato
        pose: 0
        emotion: 6
        sfxId: 
        text: Now, let's see if we vibe.
        addToLog: 1
        nextStepId: step_115
    - rid: 4444057140391575645
      type: {class: VNLineStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: step_129
        label: 
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        speakerId: Hinato
        pose: 0
        emotion: 5
        sfxId: 
        text: If we vibe, we vibe. You know what I'm saying?
        addToLog: 1
        nextStepId: step_130
    - rid: 4444057140391575646
      type: {class: VNLineStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: step_131
        label: 
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        speakerId: 
        pose: 0
        emotion: 0
        sfxId: 
        text: He then turns to you.
        addToLog: 1
        nextStepId: step_132
    - rid: 4444057140391575647
      type: {class: VNLineStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: step_141
        label: 
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        speakerId: 
        pose: 0
        emotion: 0
        sfxId: 
        text: You can hear Hinato's voice speak to you, even though he's no longer
          there.
        addToLog: 1
        nextStepId: step_142
    - rid: 4444057140391575648
      type: {class: VNLineStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: step_145
        label: 
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        speakerId: Lumis
        pose: 0
        emotion: 5
        sfxId: 
        text: Let's see what you've discovered about yourself and which faculty you
          belong to!
        addToLog: 1
        nextStepId: step_146
